22:59.295 --> 23:01.342
<i>I was trying to talk myself</i>

23:01.422 --> 23:03.844
<i>out of the voice that was deep inside myself.</i>

23:03.924 --> 23:05.767
<i>That was myself.</i>

23:06.260 --> 23:08.849
<i>I started thinking, "How dumb is this?</i>

23:08.929 --> 23:11.393
<i>Oh, God. This looks desperate."</i>

23:11.473 --> 23:14.313
<i>There I was, sitting outside
of a man's house...</i>

23:14.393 --> 23:15.689
<i>well, RV...</i>

23:15.769 --> 23:18.022
<i>trying to see if he's lying to me.</i>

23:18.731 --> 23:21.195
<i>I already knew he was lying!</i>

23:21.275 --> 23:23.364
<i>It was in my damn gut!</i>

23:23.444 --> 23:26.789
<i>And here I am trying to confirm
