23:27.990 --> 23:29.328
<i>I'm not doing this.</i>

23:45.633 --> 23:48.512
<i>There is something about my crazy.</i>

23:49.345 --> 23:50.516
<i>It's blind.</i>

23:50.596 --> 23:51.809
<i>It's not rational.</i>

23:51.889 --> 23:54.061
<i>It rages. It doesn't stop.</i>

23:54.141 --> 23:56.564
<i>It doesn't subside. It doesn't quit.</i>

23:56.644 --> 23:57.771
<i>It's immediate.</i>

24:13.494 --> 24:14.790
Robert, what was that?

24:14.870 --> 24:16.713
