24:35.641 --> 24:37.439
Is this what you do to me?

24:38.894 --> 24:40.146
Is this what you do to me?

24:40.229 --> 24:42.276
- Melinda! Melinda!
- This is what you do to me?

24:42.356 --> 24:43.983
