26:12.905 --> 26:15.124
<i>I was laid up for three weeks.</i>

26:16.116 --> 26:17.993
<i>I was in so much pain.</i>

26:18.911 --> 26:20.038
Melinda, you've been doing this

26:20.120 --> 26:21.792
