28:14.067 --> 28:17.616
<i>And somehow, that shit always worked.</i>

28:17.696 --> 28:18.948
<i>Until it didn't.</i>

28:19.823 --> 28:23.497
<i>After all, he had me by a four-letter word.</i>

28:23.577 --> 28:24.624
<i>Love.</i>

28:25.412 --> 28:27.164
<i>And I did love him.</i>

28:27.247 --> 28:31.088
<i>And that part I couldn't help,
no matter what he did.</i>

28:31.168 --> 28:34.672
<i>Love is a bitch when she's chained
to a tormentor.</i>

28:35.255 --> 28:40.261
<i>And when that tormentor is a con man,
