29:04.493 --> 29:07.916
<i>Yep... You heard me.</i>
<i>My dumb ass paid</i>

29:07.996 --> 29:10.961
<i>for his two final semesters of school.</i>

29:11.041 --> 29:14.796
<i>I was still with my man, holding him down.</i>
<i>You know?</i>

29:14.878 --> 29:17.676
<i>My lying, cheating, son of a bitch of a man.</i>

29:17.756 --> 29:19.303
- <i>There I was.</i>
