30:50.724 --> 30:51.816
<i>And yet,</i>

30:52.309 --> 30:54.273
<i>there I was, walking down the aisle</i>

30:54.353 --> 30:57.653
<i>with more questions in my head
than petals in my bouquet.</i>

30:58.940 --> 31:01.280
<i>I couldn't help but look over
at the empty seats</i>

31:01.360 --> 31:03.863
<i>where my sisters should have been sitting.</i>

31:03.945 --> 31:05.697
<i>I couldn't believe they didn't come.</i>

31:05.781 --> 31:07.202
<i>But I should have understood,</i>

31:07.282 --> 31:10.411
<i>seeing as how I wasn't even sure
why I was there.</i>

31:10.869 --> 31:12.746
<i>There was Sarah at the altar,</i>

31:12.829 --> 31:14.627
<i>my maid of honor, cheering us on.</i>

31:15.374 --> 31:17.798
<i>She loved the thought of us.
