31:54.371 --> 31:55.834
<i>from the account for something.</i>

31:55.914 --> 31:59.004
<i>Something he needed,
supplies for his battery,</i>

31:59.084 --> 32:02.179
<i>books for research, metals, plastics.
Always something.</i>

32:03.004 --> 32:06.678
<i>And as the money got low,
