32:06.758 --> 32:09.512
<i>his tolerance of me,</i>

32:10.720 --> 32:12.097
<i>his patience.</i>

32:12.722 --> 32:13.564
<i>Damn.</i>

32:14.015 --> 32:16.063
<i>Did I just say I was being tolerated?</i>

32:20.397 --> 32:22.149
I need you to see this.

32:22.232 --> 32:23.859
I mean, I'm worried.

32:25.318 --> 32:26.570
Is this right?

32:27.237 --> 32:28.238
Yeah.

32:28.780 --> 32:29.656
Damn.

32:30.991 --> 32:32.162
I'll get a job, babe.

32:32.242 --> 32:33.619
I'll try to help out.

32:34.286 --> 32:35.332
<i>"Try"?</i>

32:35.412 --> 32:37.501
<i>I couldn't believe
that bastard just said "try."</i>

32:37.581 --> 32:39.503
But you know it's gonna be
hard for me to study

32:39.583 --> 32:41.381
and work, and work on this.

32:42.210 --> 32:45.464
But I'll try. I mean, I will. I will.

32:45.547 --> 32:48.387
<i>For some reason, I just smiled.</i>

32:48.467 --> 32:49.679
I just need a little more time.

32:49.759 --> 32:50.601
Okay.

33:04.983 --> 33:06.735
- Hi, Ms. Hilderbran?
- Yes.

33:06.818 --> 33:09.116
- My name is Robert Gayle.
- I know who you are.

33:09.196 --> 33:11.449
Will you please stop calling
and writing letters?

33:12.407 --> 33:14.996
That's not how this works.
It won't get you seen.

33:15.076 --> 33:17.040
It's a lottery system for a reason.

33:17.120 --> 33:18.497
I know, but could you just...

33:23.376 --> 33:26.926
<i>Sarah helped me get a job
in her office as an office assistant.</i>

33:32.427 --> 33:34.724
They need these by morning.

33:34.804 --> 33:36.181
- Sorry.
- Sarah.

33:36.264 --> 33:38.141
It's good overtime.

33:39.434 --> 33:41.857
<i>I was actually working two jobs.</i>

33:41.937 --> 33:43.233
<i>I would leave there</i>

33:43.313 --> 33:45.156
<i>and clean offices at night.</i>

33:45.857 --> 33:47.109
<i>Anything I had to do</i>

33:47.192 --> 33:49.656
<i>to keep from having
to ask my sisters for anything.</i>

33:49.736 --> 33:50.612
<i>I just...</i>

33:51.196 --> 33:53.449
<i>I just had to get through
the next year, you know?</i>

33:53.990 --> 33:57.165
<i>I thought, "Just work hard, girl,
this man loves you."</i>

34:08.255 --> 34:09.097
Yes!

34:12.425 --> 34:13.391
Yes!

34:22.768 --> 34:23.610
Yes!

34:38.243 --> 34:39.581
- Robert.
- Baby!

34:39.661 --> 34:42.333
Robert, you have every light on
