34:50.255 --> 34:51.382
Why?

34:53.675 --> 34:54.802
Oh, my God!

35:01.641 --> 35:02.984
Sorry.

35:05.270 --> 35:07.523
<i>Not only did he almost
burn down my mother's house,</i>

35:07.606 --> 35:09.153
<i>he burned up all the wiring.</i>

35:09.441 --> 35:10.533
