35:38.470 --> 35:41.064
<i>I thought all of our troubles were over.</i>

35:41.556 --> 35:43.770
<i>I mean, he had three job interviews.</i>

35:43.850 --> 35:47.025
<i>Each started at $150,000 a year.</i>

35:47.937 --> 35:49.609
<i>I was so excited.</i>

35:49.689 --> 35:50.652
<i>But...</i>

35:50.732 --> 35:52.821
How could all three turn you down?

35:52.901 --> 35:54.278
I mean, they recruited you.

35:56.029 --> 35:57.247
When I was 15,

35:58.490 --> 36:01.244
I was in a gang,
and we robbed a grocery store.

36:02.160 --> 36:03.628
I got charged as an adult,

36:04.037 --> 36:06.506
and I spent two years in jail.

36:08.458 --> 36:10.210
I thought I could get it
expunged off my record

36:10.293 --> 36:12.967
since I was only 15, but it's still there...

36:14.881 --> 36:17.009
and no one will hire a felon.

36:17.926 --> 36:21.516
<i>You have no idea how much
I was looking forward to a break.</i>

36:21.596 --> 36:23.098
<i>Room to breathe, you know?</i>

36:23.181 --> 36:27.147
<i>To relax. Let him take care of me
for a change.</i>

36:27.227 --> 36:29.230
<i>But there I was, hearing this.</i>

36:29.729 --> 36:30.900
<i>A felon.</i>

36:30.980 --> 36:32.357
<i>And now he tells me?</i>

36:32.440 --> 36:34.909
<i>This motherfucker says this to me now!</i>

36:35.485 --> 36:37.282
<i>The con game. You see?</i>

36:37.362 --> 36:39.326
Baby, it's not the end of the world.

36:40.657 --> 36:41.954
Look, I have an idea.

36:42.450 --> 36:45.204
I figured out all the bugs,
and now it's even better than ever.

36:45.286 --> 36:46.583
I just need to get it to Prescott.

36:46.663 --> 36:48.165
I know he'll love it, okay?

36:48.248 --> 36:49.461
I'm still sending letters.

36:49.541 --> 36:50.668
I'm going by and I'm calling.

36:50.750 --> 36:52.002
And I'm gonna call his secretary.

36:52.085 --> 36:54.088
I know we're low on money.

36:54.170 --> 36:57.174
But I was thinking, if we mortgage the house,

36:57.257 --> 36:59.095
we can pay for the rest
of my research on this

36:59.175 --> 37:00.639
and make it top notch, a new design.

37:00.719 --> 37:02.392
I know it'll work.

37:03.012 --> 37:05.982
Okay. Mel, look at me. I know it'll work.

37:06.474 --> 37:07.817
- No.
- Come on.

37:08.309 --> 37:09.982
Don't stop believing in me now.

37:11.479 --> 37:13.026
Please trust me.

37:13.606 --> 37:15.859
It's gonna work, I know it will.

37:15.942 --> 37:17.034
<i>What the hell?</i>

37:17.944 --> 37:22.285
<i>I felt like my back was against the wall
and I had no choice, you know?</i>

37:22.365 --> 37:24.037
<i>I couldn't keep doing this.</i>

37:24.117 --> 37:25.664
<i>I couldn't keep working like this.</i>

37:25.744 --> 37:26.706
Come on.

37:26.786 --> 37:28.584
<i>So I had to fall for the con.</i>

37:29.122 --> 37:31.591
<i>I was in too deep to stop and walk away.</i>

37:32.625 --> 37:34.753
<i>So guess what my stupid ass did.</i>

37:36.212 --> 37:37.759
<i>My mama's house.</i>

37:38.506 --> 37:42.602
<i>A house that was paid for,
that she left to me.</i>

37:43.178 --> 37:47.058
<i>The house that she had worked
her entire life to pay for.</i>

37:48.558 --> 37:49.810
<i>I mortgaged it.</i>

37:58.026 --> 37:59.278
Melinda!

38:01.154 --> 38:04.283
<i>Working to keep my sisters
from knowing what I had done.</i>

38:05.950 --> 38:08.665
<i>And every time I would see him
sleeping in the bed</i>

38:08.745 --> 38:10.667
<i>when I was headed to one of my two jobs,</i>

38:10.747 --> 38:12.624
<i>I would get mad, you know?</i>

38:12.707 --> 38:14.459
<i>I would get resentful.</i>

38:15.627 --> 38:18.597
<i>And this was my routine every day.</i>

38:24.052 --> 38:27.056
<i>To the bastard's credit,
he did get odd jobs from time to time.</i>

38:27.138 --> 38:28.184
<i>But they...</i>

38:28.264 --> 38:31.768
<i>They didn't even cover the utilities
most of the time.</i>

38:33.269 --> 38:36.568
<i>How do two people live through two decades
and miss everything?</i>

38:36.648 --> 38:38.446
<i>Every moment of it?</i>

38:39.275 --> 38:40.613
<i>I'll tell you how.</i>

38:40.693 --> 38:42.115
<i>You just feel trapped.</i>

38:42.737 --> 38:45.536
<i>But fuck that. This trap wouldn't destroy me.</i>

38:46.115 --> 38:47.242
<i>Or did it?</i>

38:49.035 --> 38:51.629
<i>One of the saddest parts
of our lives was that</i>

38:52.163 --> 38:53.752
<i>we were just existing.</i>

38:53.832 --> 38:56.254
<i>No coloring outside of the lines,
no excitement,</i>

38:56.334 --> 38:59.964
<i>no birth of a child to mark our age,</i>

39:00.046 --> 39:04.597
<i>or his or her first step,
or his or her graduation.</i>

39:05.260 --> 39:08.514
<i>Nothing to be a mile-marker
for the years that were passing.</i>

39:09.180 --> 39:10.807
<i>There were no warning signs.</i>

39:11.766 --> 39:14.235
<i>Eighteen years seemed to pass like days.</i>

39:15.436 --> 39:17.234
<i>How does that happen?</i>

39:29.659 --> 39:30.501
Diana.

39:32.203 --> 39:33.625
Wow. You look great.

39:33.705 --> 39:35.082
Robert Gayle.

39:35.874 --> 39:37.086
How have you been?

39:37.166 --> 39:38.254
I've been good.

39:38.334 --> 39:39.547
God, I haven't seen you since...

39:39.627 --> 39:41.129
Yeah, yeah.

39:42.338 --> 39:45.183
She destroyed your RV.

39:46.050 --> 39:47.096
I don't blame her though.

39:47.176 --> 39:48.389
You should have been honest.

39:48.469 --> 39:49.687
We were kids.

39:50.138 --> 39:52.560
No, but you lied to me also, Robert.
I didn't know about her.

39:52.640 --> 39:54.354
Yeah, I know, I know, I'm sorry.

39:54.434 --> 39:56.778
Anyway, whatever happened to her?

39:57.687 --> 39:59.025
I married her.

39:59.105 --> 39:59.947
Okay.

40:00.648 --> 40:01.861
So what are you doing here?

40:01.941 --> 40:03.363
Yeah, well, get this.

40:03.443 --> 40:06.696
I've been sending letters to Prescott here
for years, telling him about my battery.

40:06.779 --> 40:08.531
You remember, in school,
what I was working on?

40:10.033 --> 40:11.621
No, sorry, I don't.

40:11.701 --> 40:13.704
Well, anyway, I've been trying to get
a meeting with him,

40:13.786 --> 40:15.834
and I found out that Ms. Hilderbran retired

40:15.914 --> 40:17.291
and that you took her place...

40:17.373 --> 40:19.420
- Congratulations, by the way.
- Mmm-hmm.

40:19.500 --> 40:22.128
So I figured this must be God
helping me out, you know?

40:22.754 --> 40:25.724
No, it's not God. I can't help you.

40:26.549 --> 40:27.596
What? Why?

40:28.051 --> 40:31.180
No, I can't. We have new policies now
about receiving information.

40:31.262 --> 40:32.889
But look, Robert, it was really...

40:32.972 --> 40:34.599
It was nice to see you.

40:35.516 --> 40:37.939
Can I take you for a coffee sometime,
maybe catch up?

40:38.019 --> 40:39.987
Yeah, sure, if you invite your wife.

40:40.730 --> 40:43.108
Look, I do not cheat on my wife.

40:43.191 --> 40:44.362
I don't do that.

40:44.442 --> 40:45.738
