40:48.863 --> 40:50.740
I know, I understand. I just...

40:51.950 --> 40:53.702
I just need some advice, that's all.

40:57.789 --> 41:00.508
Okay, look. Here's my card.

41:01.793 --> 41:03.756
I usually grab coffee at Q & A

41:03.836 --> 41:06.384
