at about 7:00 a.m.

41:06.464 --> 41:08.842
- If you happen to be there...
- Yeah.

41:08.925 --> 41:11.428
...then maybe we can talk, okay?

41:11.511 --> 41:13.933
Okay, thanks. Maybe I'll catch you there.

41:14.013 --> 41:14.855
