41:19.060 --> 41:21.779
Carly, can you get me the file
on Robert Gayle?

41:22.313 --> 41:24.235
You want the file on the psycho

41:24.315 --> 41:27.488
who's been sending letters here
since before I was born?

41:27.568 --> 41:28.990
That's what I said.

41:30.405 --> 41:31.247
Sure.

41:31.489 --> 41:32.456
Thank you.

41:41.666 --> 41:42.508
Hello?

41:42.792 --> 41:44.005
<i>Robert Gayle?</i>

41:44.085 --> 41:45.086
Yeah.

41:45.169 --> 41:46.591
<i>My name is Melvin White.</i>

41:46.671 --> 41:49.390
<i>I'm the head of security
for Prescott & Howard Industries.</i>

41:49.674 --> 41:50.845
<i>I'm calling to inform you</i>

41:50.925 --> 41:53.514
<i>that you've been put into our system
as a credible threat.</i>

41:53.594 --> 41:55.308
<i>You are not to send
another letter to our office,</i>

41:55.388 --> 41:58.061
<i>nor contact or visit
any one of our employees.</i>

41:58.141 --> 42:00.769
<i>You're not to come within
300 yards of our campus.</i>

42:00.852 --> 42:03.276
<i>If you come near the building again,
you will be arrested.</i>

42:09.152 --> 42:09.994
Fuck!

42:12.321 --> 42:13.197
Damn it!

42:22.707 --> 42:24.004
What happened?

42:27.879 --> 42:29.592
They won't see me.

42:29.672 --> 42:31.844
Prescott. They won't see me!

42:31.924 --> 42:33.551
Okay? They won't!

42:34.510 --> 42:38.810
All these years wasted!

42:45.646 --> 42:48.611
Damn it. I wanted this for us, baby.

42:48.691 --> 42:50.989
I wanted it to work for us.

42:52.904 --> 42:54.747
I wanted to get you that ring.

42:55.323 --> 42:58.413
The apartment, the boat, the private jet.

42:58.493 --> 43:00.336
I wanted you to have it all.

43:03.915 --> 43:06.043
I wanted you to have it all.

43:10.463 --> 43:12.591
Have you ever asked me what I wanted?

43:16.636 --> 43:18.889
I just want you to get a job,

43:20.098 --> 43:22.567
help me out consistently, that's all.

43:25.770 --> 43:29.570
Now that we know this battery
is not going to work...

43:31.943 --> 43:33.786
we can put it away, okay?

43:34.362 --> 43:35.908
Because that's over.

43:35.988 --> 43:37.160
That's it.

43:37.240 --> 43:39.459
Move on. Let's just move on.

43:40.368 --> 43:41.415
Okay?

43:42.662 --> 43:44.039
I know this could work.

43:44.122 --> 43:45.795
Please.

43:46.332 --> 43:47.174
Please.

43:48.292 --> 43:50.511
Please. Come on.

43:51.170 --> 43:52.592
Just a job.

43:55.925 --> 43:56.801
Okay?

43:57.927 --> 43:58.769
Yeah.

44:02.431 --> 44:04.308
I'll find the best job I can.

44:11.232 --> 44:12.279
Baby.

44:16.320 --> 44:19.244
If you give up on me now, I got nothing left.

44:22.577 --> 44:23.999
Tell me you love me.

44:28.457 --> 44:29.584
I love you.

44:31.127 --> 44:32.219
I do.

44:32.670 --> 44:34.638
But I'm so tired.

44:35.673 --> 44:37.220
I'm so tired.

44:41.804 --> 44:43.306
<i>Go, go. It's recording.</i>

44:43.389 --> 44:46.854
<i>Hi, my name is Robert Gayle,
and this is my wife, Mel.</i>

44:46.934 --> 44:49.232
<i>Hi, I'm Melinda Gayle.</i>

44:49.312 --> 44:52.191
<i>And we are excited to show you
my new invention!</i>

44:52.273 --> 44:55.277
<i>It's called the Gayle Force Wind.</i>

44:55.359 --> 44:57.362
<i>And it's powering this room right now.</i>

45:00.698 --> 45:01.665
Melinda?

45:02.867 --> 45:04.085
Melinda?

45:09.790 --> 45:11.212
Hey.

45:12.501 --> 45:15.300
Did you know this house
was about to be foreclosed on?

45:17.215 --> 45:18.057
Did you?

45:18.716 --> 45:20.179
That damn Audra at the bank.

45:20.259 --> 45:22.603
She's not supposed to be telling my business.

45:22.970 --> 45:24.438
Mel, that's our cousin.

45:25.389 --> 45:28.268
Did you know this house
was about to be foreclosed on?

45:30.561 --> 45:32.438
Yeah, I was just getting
my battery ready for...

45:32.521 --> 45:34.235
We all know about that damn battery.

45:34.315 --> 45:35.611
That shit ain't never gonna work.

45:35.691 --> 45:36.818
It's a joke.

45:37.568 --> 45:39.532
Get a job and help her.

45:39.612 --> 45:41.576
- Baby, that's enough, okay?
- Yes, Brenda, stop it.

45:41.656 --> 45:43.033
We need to be able to talk about this.

45:43.115 --> 45:45.288
Melinda, this is Mama's house.

45:45.368 --> 45:46.914
We grew up here.

45:46.994 --> 45:49.167
And you mortgaged it for him?

45:49.247 --> 45:51.043
His ass needs a job.

45:51.123 --> 45:53.296
Why are you putting up with this shit, huh?

45:53.376 --> 45:54.672
- Why?
- Brenda, let up...

45:54.752 --> 45:56.004
Move, Kalvin.

45:57.004 --> 46:00.008
The things our daddy did to keep this house.

46:00.091 --> 46:02.094
And you gonna lose it?

46:02.677 --> 46:03.848
I knew this would happen.

46:03.928 --> 46:05.725
- Okay, okay. Listen.
- I knew it.

46:05.805 --> 46:07.852
We know the problem,
