46:32.832 --> 46:33.799
Just listen.

46:35.334 --> 46:36.461
Look, man.

46:36.752 --> 46:40.177
All we need you to do is help us
keep the requirements, all right?

46:41.215 --> 46:44.013
You gotta drive and you gotta
be on time to his chains.

46:44.093 --> 46:45.220
That's all.

46:45.303 --> 46:47.642
We can get this paid back in, like,
three months.

46:47.722 --> 46:48.849
But you can't be late.

46:48.931 --> 46:51.685
You can't miss a delivery or a pickup,
or we'll lose everything.

46:51.767 --> 46:53.019
Everything!

46:54.603 --> 46:56.856
- And we can't pay you.
- And we shouldn't do it.

46:56.939 --> 46:59.737
He don't give a damn about nothing
and nobody but himself.

46:59.817 --> 47:01.864
Look, promise us that you'll do this, Robert.

47:01.944 --> 47:03.947
And you'll do this right.

47:04.030 --> 47:05.282
Promise us.

47:10.828 --> 47:11.670
Yeah.

47:12.830 --> 47:13.672
I'm in.

47:14.498 --> 47:16.170
See, he's in.

47:16.250 --> 47:18.844
I'll see you at the lot
at 6:00 a.m. tomorrow.

47:19.337 --> 47:20.304
I'm there.

47:21.130 --> 47:22.718
And I'm changing the locks.

47:22.798 --> 47:24.512
Mel, we're just trying to help.

47:24.592 --> 47:25.638
Mmm-hmm.

47:25.718 --> 47:27.181
She gotta want to help herself.

47:27.261 --> 47:28.262
You're right.

47:28.346 --> 47:29.308
- Have a good night.
- 6:00 a.m.

47:29.388 --> 47:31.061
He'll be there. Just go.

47:37.313 --> 47:40.158
You know why I know how you don't
love me the same?

47:42.026 --> 47:44.450
