48:39.875 --> 48:42.173
<i>Another night of him sleeping downstairs.</i>

48:44.255 --> 48:45.973
<i>At first, I was sad about it.</i>

48:47.174 --> 48:48.892
<i>Then I started to get mad.</i>

48:49.593 --> 48:51.182
<i>It's good.</i>

48:51.262 --> 48:53.726
Right? I mean, it's good.
