01:01:27.434 --> 01:01:28.276
No.

01:01:29.269 --> 01:01:30.691
<i>I wasn't.</i>

01:01:31.938 --> 01:01:34.032
<i>I was in that place that scares me.</i>

01:01:35.233 --> 01:01:37.327
<i>That place between present and furious.</i>

01:01:37.819 --> 01:01:39.696
<i>I had lost all rhyme and reason.</i>

01:01:40.614 --> 01:01:43.078
<i>It's like nothing mattered but getting even.</i>

01:01:43.158 --> 01:01:46.456
<i>I was told I get it from my daddy,
